Detailed Description

Database Definition Parser.

Parses a supplied database definition, and transforms it to a list of tokens. The returned tokens can be passed to CodeGenVars() to generate a variable tree that can be used for code generation.

Parses a database definition (fragment) and adds the scanned tokens.

The database definition file content may be supplied in whole or in smaller fragments, e.g. parsed line by line, to avoid reading the entire definition in memory.
